snippet.title: THEMIS - Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome, Awakened. Your task is simple, yet the stakes have never been higher. Will you yield to The First One's will or defy your fate dictated by the new laws of the Metaspace? The choice is yours.

THEMIS - an upcoming puzzle platformer game from Carp Games Studio, aiming at challenging both your reflexes and the brain cells.
